fulltitle: Dick Hyman part 2 interview by Monk Rowe - 3/17/2001 - Clearwater Beach, FL
description:
In our second interview, Dick Hyman talks about film scoring with Woody Allen, the active NYC studio scene, recording early rock & roll, and his personal favorites in the music world.
